Richard Crane (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Richard_Crane_(actor) 0 Richard Ollie Crane (June 6, 1918 – March 9, 1969) was a veteran character actor whose career spanned three decades in films and television. His early career included many uncredited performances in feature films made in the 1940s.
